name: Hassan of the Serenity 6 outfits (Fate) 静谧哈桑 6套外观
description:
このLoRAモデルを使用して画像を生成し、インターネット上で公開する際に、他の人が簡単に見つけられるように、原作者とモデルのウェブサイトを明記していただけると、非常に感謝いたします

当您使用此LoRA模型生成图片并发布在网上，希望可以注明一下该模型的原网址和作者方便他人查找，谢谢

When you use this LoRA model to generate images and publish them online, I would greatly appreciate it if you could indicate the original website and author of the model to make it easier for others to find.

-

LoRA of Hassan(Serenity)

静谧哈桑的lora

-

works around 0.7-0.9, support 4 sets of official outfit, and 2 sets of cosplay

推荐权重0.7-0.9 支持4套官方外观和2套变装

-

Default默认=Default, SerenityOutfit

Prototype Outfit 苍银 便服= Prototype, OriginalDress

Poisonous Flower Blooming at Night 灵衣-毒之花=PFBN, ExtraOutfit, see-through

Merry Sheep欢悦绵羊=MerrySheep, XmasCostume

dangerous beast危险野兽=DBcos, BeastCosplay

royal icing皇家糖霜=RoyalIce, LancerAlterClothing, sleeveless, dark-skin female

-

Feel free to post any idea or character model request in the Discussion

有模型的需求可以B站私信或者在这里留言给我

id：不吃青蛙的阿龙

有空就会做

If you like my work, feel free to support me on patreon.com/RiuKiMK1

or RiuKi_MK1 is Creating AI artworks, LoRa models (buymeacoffee.com)
